    "In contrast, multi-platform integrated development environments such as Flutter or Microsoft Visual Studio support multiple programming languages.",
    "In light of this, ChatGPT employs machine learning and natural language processing technologies to accurately interpret and respond to user inputs expressed in colloquial language.",
    "In contrast to conventional programming languages, which adhere to particular syntax and principles, ChatGPT is designed to comprehend user inquiries and provide appropriate responses, as explained by OpenAI (2023).",
